    <summary>Git for AI memory — persistent context across Claude, GPT, Cursor, Windsurf and more</summary>
    <description>
memgit gives your AI assistants persistent, version-controlled memory that follows you across tools.

Switch from Claude to Cursor to ChatGPT mid-project and your context is already there.

## Features
- One command to register with all AI tools: `memgit setup all`
- Works with Claude Code, Claude Desktop, Cursor, Windsurf, Cline, Continue.dev
- GPT Custom Actions and Gemini via HTTP server mode
- BM25 search across all stored memories
- Git-like version history — checkpoint, branch, diff

## Quick start
```
memgit init
memgit setup all
memgit sync
```
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/code4161/memgit/releases</releaseNotes>
